			class Attributes
			{
				init="[intel0,""Lieutenant Niko, your orders are to remain in your position and defend the high-ground. If the CSAT attempt to assault, we will send reinforcements from the reserves south of us. When you have secured your position, send a runner to my position at Outpost Dana. He will find me in the HQ building on the south end of the outpost. Signed Captain Papalous""] remoteExec [""ace_intelitems_fnc_setObjectData"",0];";
